Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:34.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A rage that is only\npermitted by youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:40.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A pure, unadulterated rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:45.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is the most appropriate description for\nthe emotion expressed by the young soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:47.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How exquisite it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How I desire it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:52.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:06.77,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,352)\fad(0,1600)}Act 18:\NThe Duel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:14.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, baby, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:05.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you are a soldier's son that\nyou did not give in to fear and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:35.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond... is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:39.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This body retains only his\nshape and appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:45.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There is no longer anything\nof Edmond himself left within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:53.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you proof that Edmond,\nthe man you once loved, is now dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:56.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:20.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cutting it pretty close...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:30.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote a message in\na birthday card for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:36.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I think we're too old for that kind of thing,\nso I feel awkward giving it to him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:40.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, give it to Albert\nafter I leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please?\NI'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:46.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He should just be a man\nand give it to him himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...\NIt can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:40.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast, Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:44.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be...\NHe's only a...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:44.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Madame, but I\ncan't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:52.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me go! I have a duty\nto keep that boy safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:55.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please understand,\nthis is a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:59.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A formal duel, in which Monsieur Albert\nchallenged the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:05.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert is... Albert is still a child!\NCall it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:10.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, Madame. Monsieur Albert\nholds the rank of viscount.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:14.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the eyes of the law, this duel\nis completely legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:23.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your loneliness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:36.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... I'll bear the brunt\nof all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:13.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Countess Morcerf!\NWatch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:19.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Watch as I prove to you that\NEdmond Dantes is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:26.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you\nwake me up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:57.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I've been\nwaiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:05.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To become Gankutsuou is\nto lose your humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As the composition of his entire body\nis being replaced with crystal,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the temperature of his heart\ndrops and drops,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...until it, too,\nis eventually lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:19.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The instant he is released from his suffering,\nhe will also lose his emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anger... sadness...\Nhatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:26.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He will lose\nthem all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is what he fears\nabove all else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:37.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is why his heart\nis the last part of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:42.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If he still retains even fragments\nof human emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:45.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...his heart alone will\nbe vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gankutsuou, come closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:58.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...\NCome straight at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:04.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:06.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will now prove who\nthe victor is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were cursed\nsince birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:13.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...born from the union of that cowardly\ntraitor Fernand Mondego and Mercedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You, who have walked in the sunlight your\nentire life, could not possibly know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:23.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the tale of the innocent man who\nhad his youth stolen away from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:26.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the old man who fell victim\nto loneliness and starvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:32.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fate has now come full circle, and the\ncurse is about to reach its fruition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:41.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Curse your fate, and your parents,\nas you die by my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,FRANZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope he likes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:14.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:20.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The... The doctor's gonna be here soon,\nso hang in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:28.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, you were out cold\nlast night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Those pills worked pretty good,\ndidn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:37.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:45.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... that things\nturned out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:59.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you taught me how to handle a sword,\nso I put up a pretty good fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:05.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... Don't try to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:14.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot... You think you\ncan boss me around?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:16.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:18.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:30.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:37.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was last year...\NOr was it the year before last?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:43.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us and Eugenie went\nto Normandy together, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:50.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, or was it in the\nsouth of France?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:55.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us sprawled out\non the beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:00.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and we celebrated\nyour birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:08.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was so windy that when we tried to eat\na piece of cheese, it tasted like sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:18.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And Eugenie's favorite hat blew away...\NShe was really depressed about it, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:27.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:35.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on\nturning sixteen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:48.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz, hang on\na little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:54.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor's gonna be here\nany minute now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:21:00.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be okay.\NYou're gonna be okay, so hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:09.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Franz?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:14.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice and warm out here,\nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:40.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,FRANZ!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:13.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alone, I walk through the\ndarkness of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:15.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as I wait for the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:18.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, act 19:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:20.92,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,352)}Act 19:\NEven if I Should Stop Being Me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:21.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."Even if I Should Stop Being Me."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.74,0:23:24.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
